{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "希里丝（铳士Ver.） 第2话 守护的铳声",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "好……似乎赶在熊之前\\n回到村里了！\\n接下来只要有铳……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊……希里丝！？\\n不是不能用铳吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "是不能用……不过等下再解释！\\n现在无论如何都少不了它！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "少不了它？你要用它做什么……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族们",
            "context": "有熊！朝村落这边来了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "它好像来了！一会儿再解释！\\n梅露莎，我们走！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "熊",
            "context": "呼……呼！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "等等，求你了，千万别来村里……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "熊",
            "context": "咕嗷嗷嗷！嘎嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "糟糕，朝这边来了！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "大叔……快趴下！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "熊",
            "context": "咕噜！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "怎么样？怕了吧！\\n那就……再来一发！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "熊",
            "context": "咕噜！？\\n呜嗷嗷嗷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "呼……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "熊被铳击吓跑了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "竟然用铳对付熊！\\n你怎么能用人造的东西\\n夺取大自然一份子的生命……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我对用铳这事向你们道歉……\\n但是！大叔你不是说不想\\n无端剥夺动物的生命吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我用铳正是因为……\\n这样才能如大叔所愿啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "什么？\\n你说如我所愿？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "嗯，我看那头熊对声音很敏感\\n就忽然想到，如果它听见巨响，\\n也许就会觉得这里很危险。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "的、的确……那么大的声音\\n不曾出现在森隐族的生活里……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "对吧？正因为这样，\\n才使得一些动物难以对这个\\n宁静的村落抱有警戒心。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "警戒心……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110270_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅露莎",
            "context": "就是说，你是要让它明白这里\\n是会发出非自然界声响的地方……\\n是个危险的地方，对吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "嗯。这样一来，野兽们\\n闯进村落的频率也会减少，\\n所以很抱歉……我就用铳了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "为了保护大叔你们\\n所珍视的动物……保护“自然”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "你是为了保护自然\\n才用了人类的战争工具吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "对，铳如果用对了地方也能成为\\n保护野兽的力量……大叔你既然\\n熟知野兽的习性，应该能理解吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "是啊……\\n如果只靠森隐族的常识，\\n的确保护不了刚才那头熊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "保护了那头熊的，\\n不是森隐族的规矩，\\n而是你……和那把铳。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "大叔……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "也许……我对人类文明\\n过于警戒了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "你叫希里丝吧。\\n如果你愿意……\\n能定期来这村落附近狩猎吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "森隐族男子",
            "context": "如果野兽记住了铳声，\\n和人之间的界线就能更加明确。\\n这样也是间接地保护了它们。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "嗯，我当然愿意！\\n为了保护这片森林里的野兽，\\n我会小心地进行狩猎的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "呼……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01",
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喔……你状态不错嘛，\\n希里丝。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊，本来你的弓箭水平就很厉害，\\n现在又有了用铳的才能。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，卢卡哥哥……\\n你们怎么来射击场了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我们听说你在森隐族村落的\\n那场熊的骚动中大显身手来着？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "哦，之前那事啊？诶嘿嘿，\\n还好啦，可以说是努力了一把！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是吗，谢谢你。\\n那个村落一直都挺避讳人类的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "多亏了你，他们也肯\\n与我们进行一些交流了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "用人类文明保护森隐族文明……\\n希里丝你这主意真了不起。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诶嘿嘿，听你这么说我很开心！\\n那件事让我也意识到了\\n很重要的一点。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "很重要的一点？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "嗯！就是理解不同种族\\n与地域的文化非常重要！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "有朝一日我想要建立村落，\\n自己当族长。为此，\\n我想进一步了解外界的文化。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "这样一来……我就能当个\\n更了不起的族长了吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来如此，那倒是正好。\\n你觉得怎么样，卢卡？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喂喂……你真要让我\\n和这家伙一起北行啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "北行？\\n你们两个在说什么啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，有一件事想拜托你。\\n现在我们和北格拉斯迪亚大陆的交流\\n不是开始多起来了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以想让卢卡去北大陆的\\n城市看看，顺便视察。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就想问你愿不愿意\\n和他同行。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "诶！？北大陆的城市？好棒！\\n我还没去过呢！我要去我要去！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "真是的，反正你去了\\n也只会成天吵着说冷，\\n我看你还是算了吧……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "呃啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "我已经不是只会吵闹的小孩子了！\\n这可是难得能学习\\n各种文化的机会，我一定要去！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊哈哈，你很感兴趣嘛。\\n那这件事就交给卢卡和希里丝了，\\n诺艾尔会为你们带路的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "唉……真没辙，不过这和\\n出个小远门也没什么两样，\\n去就去吧。你可小心别走丢了啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100029_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "希里丝",
            "context": "才不会呢！我决定了……\\n我要好好学习北大陆的文化！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}